{
  "texts": [
    "Deep learningTo establish more robust semantic connections between natural language queries and code, researchers have increasingly turned to deep learning models to tackle code search tasks.",
    "The fundamental approach involves encoding both the query statement and code into separate vector representations, then assessing the semantic correlation between the two through vector similarity analysis.",
    "Gu et al. [19] innovatively employed perceptrons and RNNs to embed various code elements such as method names, API call sequences, and code sequences into a shared high-dimensional space.",
    "This lays the foundation for DeepCS, a code search tool.",
    "Sachdev et al. [128] introduced neural code search (NCS), tailored for extensive code repositories."
  ]
}